in the machine?

39:11.252 --> 39:14.153
Those aren't mine.
Baz is blue.

39:15.657 --> 39:17.089
Oh.

39:19.193 --> 39:20.893
Sorry, baby.

39:22.864 --> 39:26.866
Hey, that suit looks
really good on you.

39:26.868 --> 39:29.669
Thanks.

39:29.671 --> 39:30.870
You want a hit?

39:30.872 --> 39:31.937
No, thanks.

39:31.939 --> 39:34.373
[ Water splashes ]

39:38.412 --> 39:40.746
I'm really happy
you're doing this job

39:40.748 --> 39:42.381
with your brothers.

39:44.151 --> 39:46.853
I think it's gonna go
really well.

39:50.024 --> 39:52.358
Why do you call him that?

39:52.360 --> 39:54.026
What?

39:54.028 --> 39:57.563
Baz.
You know he's not my brother.

39:57.565 --> 39:58.898
Okay, but...

39:58.900 --> 40:00.566
I mean,
he's been with us for years.

40:00.568 --> 40:02.468
He's family.

40:10.912 --> 40:12.311
Cannonball!

40:12.313 --> 40:15.047
Aaah!

40:15.049 --> 40:17.049
[ Julia laughs ]

40:17.051 --> 40:18.384
I bet I can make a bigger splash
than you.

40:18.386 --> 40:20.852
-Oh, you're on.
-Let's see!

40:20.854 --> 40:24.790
[ Water splashes ]

40:24.792 --> 40:26.926
Julia: Whoo!

40:26.928 --> 40:30.596
♪♪

40:30.598 --> 40:31.931
Let's see it!

40:31.933 --> 40:33.799
Whoo!

