like that?

41:27.721 --> 41:30.456
No.

41:30.458 --> 41:32.592
Are you sure?

41:32.594 --> 41:34.260
I'm sure.

42:35.323 --> 42:37.122
I want you
to take the bed.

42:37.124 --> 42:39.391
I'll sleep
on the couch.

